{"tid":213647,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 嫌錢腥？傳 Chrome 將預設廣告阻擋功能","createTime":"2017-04-23T09:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T05:30:10.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb98d86ace18f13fc2982600b5e582f0ec4ad7f","tid":213647,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Google 嫌錢腥？傳 Chrome 將預設廣告阻擋功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/04/20/chrome-may-comes-with-ad-blocker-as-default/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F04%2F20%2Fchrome-may-comes-with-ad-blocker-as-default%2Fsoftware%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=72c504e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/20/chrome-may-comes-with-ad-blocker-as-default/software/</a></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n網上廣告是搜尋器服務供應商 Google 的主要收入來源，驟眼看來以「嫌錢腥」去形容他們可能非常貼切，因為華爾街日報剛剛刊登了文章，指出 Google 正準備為他們的瀏覽器軟件 Chrome 加入阻隔廣告（ad-blocker）功能，可算跟自己的主要收入途徑打對台，實際則可能是完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/0421-1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F0421-1a.jpg&h=b6e2fd71&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n一般相信 Google 並非真的有意將自己銷售的廣告阻隔，而是透過開發，並且在 Chrome 預設廣告阻隔功能，吸引用戶放棄使用現有的第三方廣告阻隔插件。為了要令 Google 的廣告內容加入這些第三方插件的白名單，繞過它們的封阻，Google 需要支付他們大量金錢。換句話說，Google 自家的廣告阻隔功能將會預設開啟，並提供阻隔彈出式廣告視窗、自動播放影音等擾人內容的功能，這樣的話 Google 就能減低第三方廣告阻隔插件的議價能力。<br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報指 Google 還未落實今次計劃，假如最後決定推出，或者會在 5 月中舉行的 Google I/O 上正式宣佈。<br />\n<br />\n來源：techcrunch"},{"pid":"fa41009818b80f7994af472c5ca5121b8e5398ac","tid":213647,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:02:51.000Z","msg":"If you can't beat them<br />\njoin them<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede29f76fb716d0705ed5cfb136170141df97a64","tid":213647,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"d人del曬adblocks之後咪任佢魚肉，橫掂個廣告阻擋功能係chrome整既，有陰毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dee9e384c39d0be92acd01227c6346d57258fc5","tid":213647,"uid":77689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"Block哂其他廣告, 放生自己, 咁就可以迫廣告公司一定要經Google落廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}